# =============================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# =============================================================================
# 
# 1. Services not showing up?
#    - Verify the service is enabled: true
#    - Check that authentication credentials (token/api_key) are correct
#    - Ensure URLs are accessible from the machine running motd
#    - Run with debug mode: ./motd -d
# 
# 2. Bandwidth not showing?
#    - Install vnstat: sudo apt install vnstat (Ubuntu/Debian)
#    - Initialize vnstat database: sudo vnstat -u -i eth0
#    - Check interface name with: ip link show
#    - Verify interface is configured correctly in this file
#    - Bandwidth is always displayed as monthly data with 30-day estimates
# 
# 3. Docker containers not showing?
#    - Install Docker and ensure user has permissions
#    - Verify compose_dir path is correct
#    - Check that docker ps works manually
# 
# 4. Disk usage not showing for tank?
#    - Verify tank_mount path exists and is mounted
#    - Check with: df -h /mnt/tank (or your path)
#    - Ensure mount point is accessible
# 
# 5. Temperature not showing?
#    - Install lm-sensors: sudo apt install lm-sensors
#    - Run sensor detection: sudo sensors-detect
#    - Verify with: sensors command
# =============================================================================